{"tid":1486123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非完就應該set 死線要求政府回應 否則全面升級","createTime":"2019-08-18T18:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T06:36:09.000Z","uid":128516,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"13a51f9a29bf51e49dbc64c5616875cbd41692ac","tid":1486123,"uid":128516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:41:05.000Z","msg":"又一次過百萬人上街<br />\n政府竟然未開始就針對同遺憾<br />\n完左無野挑剔就話影響主要幹道<br />\n完全無理會過遊行訴求<br />\n政府成日讉責暴力<br />\n但和理非又得到d咩?<br />\n<br />\n我地要好似運動初期咁<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非-&gt;set deadline-&gt;升級<br />\n再set 限期deadline 要求政府回應<br />\n否則無論係和理非定勇武層面升級<br />\n再次撼動政府甚至中央同國際</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4b974975ecbb563c694a63af04c19cdcf5c5ee76","tid":1486123,"uid":128516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:41:23.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24efa0436f9745064c43e4ed77051112534e9c53","tid":1486123,"uid":128516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:41:37.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2916273e52d4ee330b5c5a1f9eb940da53857280","tid":1486123,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a119a6245197e5be1e042cdb3451f82fdac3d9","tid":1486123,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13a51f9a29bf51e49dbc64c5616875cbd41692ac","tid":1486123,"uid":128516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:41:05.000Z","msg":"又一次過百萬人上街<br />\n政府竟然未開始就針對同遺憾<br />\n完左無野挑剔就話影響主要幹道<br />\n完全無理會過遊行訴求<br />\n政府成日讉責暴力<br />\n但和理非又得到d咩?<br />\n<br />\n我地要好似運動初期咁<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非-&gt;set deadline-&gt;升級<br />\n再set 限期deadline 要求政府回應<br />\n否則無論係和理非定勇武層面升級<br />\n再次撼動政府甚至中央同國際</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:42:06.000Z","msg":"重申七一宣言，設立死線<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#五大訴求<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#解散警隊<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"3daa1ec3ed7dccda71e2448c8c6bceab083c0888","tid":1486123,"uid":101057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:42:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a8f56f35d30d0793320aaae836a46f8161e99bf","tid":1486123,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:42:17.000Z","msg":"set死線啊!<br />\n<br />\n已經有手足組織9月頭三罷"},{"pid":"490509602ff107503da035240d07cc33ded444ee","tid":1486123,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:42:20.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要說「推」，試著說「８２３人鏈」<br />\n<br />\n８２３人鏈：香港之路Hong Kong Way正！式！上！線！！！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486119</a>"},{"pid":"dabec9feb4eab043391a31f73dde30080fa6f934","tid":1486123,"uid":85930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:42:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6328569dfc18301b63fae93723b63dd402f72085","tid":1486123,"uid":236240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:42:31.000Z","msg":"同意！推"},{"pid":"1d0120f432b22c3df7c5b94be664c4269a3fa23c","tid":1486123,"uid":128516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:42:51.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eeaf7efb2deabb9753d707ec10402b3efc2d9df","tid":1486123,"uid":128516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:45:27.000Z","msg":"記住<br />\n今次和理非唔係要勇武交返個波比和理非<br />\n亦唔係要起大台<br />\n而係要話比政府 林鄭 全世界知<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>過去一個月勇武派既行動無令到民意逆轉減退<br />\n和理非同勇武繼續CONNECT<br />\n絕不割蓆</strong></span></span><br />\n大家向住同一個目標進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf410fec9f0cf1807a8c80d70080c55f52fd03a8","tid":1486123,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:45:51.000Z","msg":"升級完又降返級<br />\n無限輪迴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9088d6fd7e8710d98bc5e78d7da6c2e001a7db26","tid":1486123,"uid":128516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:45:53.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0f12f24c9b88e43f310306203b73976b01a72f3c","tid":1486123,"uid":128516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:46:05.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7c4388d00f9b8ab54fa98c87c766fba26f87ce","tid":1486123,"uid":128516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:47:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和理非-&gt;SET 死線-&gt;升級<br />\n<br />\n政府唔回應就勇武同和理非一齊升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"91142f5b6a281761daa756e5e47130e2ec128e73","tid":1486123,"uid":128516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:47:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和理非-&gt;SET 死線-&gt;升級<br />\n<br />\n政府唔